'''新加坡金融管理局'''，简称'''新加坡金管局'''（{{lang-en|'''M'''onetary '''A'''uthority of '''S'''ingapore}}，简称：'''MAS'''），是[[新加坡|新加坡]]行使[[中央银行|中央银行]]职能的政府机构，同时也是负责监控[[金融机构|金融机构]]的主管部门，其在行政上向[[新加坡总理|新加坡总理]]负责<ref name="aboutmas">{{Cite web
|url = http://www.mas.gov.sg/About-MAS.aspx
|format = 
|title = About MAS
|author = 
|date = 2014-07-14
|publisher = 新加坡金融管理局官网
|language = en
|accessdate = 2014-11-22
|quote = As Singapore's central bank, the Monetary Authority of Singapore (MAS) promotes sustained, non-inflationary economic growth through appropriate monetary policy formulation and close macroeconomic surveillance of emerging trends and potential vulnerabilities. It manages Singapore's exchange rate, foreign reserves and liquidity in the banking sector. MAS is also an integrated supervisor overseeing all financial institutions in Singapore -- banks, insurers, capital market intermediaries, financial advisors, and the stock exchange. With its mandate to foster a sound and progressive financial services sector in Singapore, MAS also helps shape Singapore's financial industry by promoting a strong corporate governance framework and close adherence to international accounting standards. In addition, it spearheads retail investor education. MAS ensures that Singapore's financial industry remains vibrant, dynamic and competitive by working closely with other government agencies and financial institutions to develop and promote Singapore as a regional and international financial centre.
|archive-date = 2021-02-07
|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210207184344/https://www.mas.gov.sg/About-MAS.aspx
|dead-url = no
}}</ref>。金管局现任董事会主席为[[尚达曼|尚达曼]]，於2011年5月任职<ref name=zhuxi/> 。

== 历史 ==

{{参见|新加坡历史|亞洲四小龍}}

[[新加坡|新加坡]]在1970年以前，其国内与央行相关的各种货币职能由多个政府部门和机构负责管理。但随着新加坡的[[亞洲四小龍|经济腾飞]]，[[全球金融体系|国际金融环境]]也日益复杂，对于金融主管机构的职权进行厘清与精简化势在必行。于是在1970年[[新加坡国会|新加坡国会]]通过了《新加坡金融管理局法令》<ref name="MASact">{{Cite web
|url = http://statutes.agc.gov.sg/aol/search/display/view.w3p;page=0;query=DocId%3A8cde6c10-335e-4415-b97a-62aa88a1be3f%20Depth%3A0%20Status%3Ainforce;rec=0;whole=yes
|format = 
|title = 《Monetary Authority of Singapore Act》
|author = 
|date = 1999-12-30
|publisher = [[新加坡国会|新加坡国会]]
|language = en
|accessdate = 2014-11-22
|quote = .
|archive-date = 2018-02-12
|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180212145356/http://statutes.agc.gov.sg/aol/search/display/view.w3p;page=0;query=DocId:8cde6c10-335e-4415-b97a-62aa88a1be3f%20Depth:0%20Status:inforce;rec=0;whole=yes
|dead-url = no
}}</ref>，翌年1971年1月1日“新加坡金融管理局”正式成立，开始行使[[中央银行|中央银行]]与金融监管职能。<ref name="lishimain">{{Cite web
 |url          = http://www.mas.gov.sg/About-MAS/Overview.aspx
